reviews.review_text:
my favorite of the 3 night Hampton 1988 run - after the fact During the run I thought that the middle night was better, yet when I choose my favorite to listen to ever since the next week, I chose this one.  

I taped this entire run(through Malcom Kaplan's mics & through a pretty good FM 'boom box' (actually the speakers were detachable).
